- **Response Section**: Fade-in animated card styled neatly with the Shloka (Sanskrit + Transliteration) and sections cleanly separated by dividers. Provide secondary Shlokas ("Also relevant") below the main AI response.
- **Footer**: Proper disclaimers.
- Handle state management for loading, inputs, and selected language. All hardcoded tags and strings will have English/Hindi variants.

