## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Test API endpoint using mock parameters to verify fallback logic.

### Manual Verification
- Verify the English to Hindi language switch updates all UI text and the placeholder text strings simultaneously.
- Verify `findRelevantShlokas` returns the appropriate shloka for diverse queries.
- Ensure the app is correctly laid out and fits exactly right on a simulated 375px wide mobile device without horizontal overflow.
- Ensure the user secret `GEMINI_API_KEY` is completely out of the client bundle.
